# ╔═╡ 8c0672a6-0b88-4fb7-8c51-01d3e36d2236
md"## Part 1
How many characters need to be processed before the first start-of-packet marker is detected?

Start-of-packet marker is a sequence of 4 distinct characters."

# ╔═╡ 691ff5bf-fc36-418c-a49d-04f18f58edca
function find_packet_start(input)
	for i in 1:length(input)
		if allunique(input[i:i+3])
			return i + 3
		end
	end
end

# ╔═╡ e458e6f7-bd7e-4350-9b99-16888bdac1d9
find_packet_start(input)

# ╔═╡ 117da1d3-f170-4826-8c75-be51c0bcfe55
md"## Part 2
How many characters need to be processed before the first start-of-message marker is detected?

Start-of-message marker is 14 distinct characters."

# ╔═╡ 9f32d9a5-0ed3-4eba-87e2-fe6c529e9fdf
function find_message_start(input)
	for i in 1:length(input)
		if allunique(input[i:i+13])
			return i + 13
		end
	end
end

# ╔═╡ 0025e225-ccc9-4917-8fe2-1c6d4e16b864
find_message_start(input)

